    <text>
        <body>
        <div type="letter">
           <opener><dateline><date when="1917-07-14">October 19, 1917.<dateline></date><salute>Dear <persName key="harriet-monroe">Harriet</persName>:</salute>
        </opener>
            <p>
                Be sure and send the proof of my article on <persName key="louis_untermeyer">Louis Untermeyer</persName>’s <title key="theseTimes">book</title>, won’t you, because there is one sentence I want to delete.</p>
                <p>I saw little <persName key="ricahrd_hunt">Hunt</persName> last night, and he said you were very kind to him in <placeName key="Chicago">Chicago</placeName>, and he had a beautiful time.</p>
                <closer>Affectionately yours,</closer>
          
            </div>
        </body>
